two kinds of unit tests

1. Internal (add main.c to primary glshim sources).
   Replace LOAD_GLES with a no-op.
   Provide global gles functions (can I do this automatically?).
   How do I mock existing functions? Defines? mock.h

2. GL/ES reference blocks:

    GL_BLOCK
        glBegin();
        glVertex2f();
        glEnd();
    GLES_BLOCK
        glEnableClientState(GL_VERTEX_ARRAY);
        glDrawArrays(1, 2, 3, 4);
        glDisableClientState(GL_VERTEX_ARRAY);
    END_BLOCK

